Actually would recommend just use it at home and also the app tries to Prevent you from using it somewhere else because you have to set your home location and unless there's no bug introduced into your car Which also happened in the past by different manufacturers where it wasn't updating the location anymore You might run into the issue of blocking fees at public charging stations. So at public charging stations that would not be optimal. If you go to friends houses you can still change your home location for if you're there for a longer time.

