So that's currently in heavy discussion also in the development teams and where we are also currently evaluating a lot the customer feedback, what is interesting for them, what not, what do you actually want to see. So if you have feedback on that, also just hand it in. We are happy to know what you actually want to see also in the app.

**Speaker 2** _[27:04]_

How do you offset the opportunity costs of EVs blocking charging points longer so the infrastructure cost of? The charger that could charge another EV in the meantime so so

