**Speaker 1** _[27:30]_

Yeah, so we tried to not to. Actually it prolongs the battery life if actually you set your target SSC not to a hundred percent or the minimum SSC to zero.

**Speaker 2** _[27:43]_

Okay, last question. I assume your data processing happens in the cloud. What's the latency and how does it affect the dynamic charging? Oh, another question just coming in.

